Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:30.53,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Then I noticed the fact there was no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:30.53,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}až som si uvedomila že môj čas vypršal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:38.71,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}I was a believer in life to be myself always,
