Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:45.67,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}and was asking whether I would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:45.67,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}a pýtala som sa ho, či ešte môžem žiť.
